Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US reviews Soviet military strength
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wjkj
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Oct 1981
Bias questions over US report on Soviet military strength. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.